data.description: Spacious 4 Bedroom townhome that backs to a preserve area. Master bedroom is located on the first floor. Guest 1/2 bath downstairs. Townhome has tall volume ceilings with high windows that allow for plenty of natural light. Upstairs bedrooms are generous in size and walkway open to downstairs. Unit has an attached 1 car garage. Community has a pool and is gated for security. Conveniently close to shopping and dining. Entertainment center in living room will convey with the property. rmszappr&sub2err
